{"tid":2201658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：劉公子探快必 嘆「成個人瘦晒」（李八方）","createTime":"2020-09-14T03:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T06:00:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34a6734d39fb70f79f34bc23fc8b2859da29d3de","tid":2201658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/IA57PKKEIBFHVBRBK3T6NLNQNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FIA57PKKEIBFHVBRBK3T6NLNQNA%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Of4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=f7ac5833\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FIA57PKKEIBFHVBRBK3T6NLNQNA%2F&h=2f827211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/IA57PKKEIBFHVBRBK3T6NLNQNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：劉公子探快必 嘆「成個人瘦晒」（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xY-tknTzpEOPG0Y06Hl61cDaG8A=/1851x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AG2M32JU5JCL3BFCEZK6VXUA2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxY-tknTzpEOPG0Y06Hl61cDaG8A%3D%2F1851x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAG2M32JU5JCL3BFCEZK6VXUA2A.jpg&h=a8de935b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉公子（左）喺7.1被捕，事後係快必陪佢去「踢保」。<br />\n<br />\n人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志畀國安處人員以發表煽動文字罪拘捕，仲要唔畀保釋，扣押係荔枝角收押所已經五日。之前不時參加抗爭活動、曾經同快必一齊被拉嘅深黃同志富商「劉公子」劉定成，最近探過快必，劉公子話快必雖然仲堅強同情緒ok，但收押所食物好差，快必冇乜點食嘢，搞到成個人瘦晒。<br />\n<br />\n劉公子喺7.1時同擺街站嘅快必及慢必一齊被警方拘捕，事後仲係快必陪佢去「踢保」，兩個算係一齊抗爭過，所以今年70歲嘅劉公子知道快必被拉同扣押之後，非常擔心戰友情況，前日同張大衛牧師前往探快必。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e4orIHRIirZ30kA2DBpj6xSDCWY=/1490x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YHEEYY3SMRG3ROYMVDZ57YLPLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe4orIHRIirZ30kA2DBpj6xSDCWY%3D%2F1490x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYHEEYY3SMRG3ROYMVDZ57YLPLM.jpg&h=8311d1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■噚日慢必（右）開街站，劉公子都有去撐場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撐慢必街站<br />\n<br />\n快必目前被單獨囚禁喺荔枝角收押所幾十呎嘅房間內，劉公子同八方講，因為每日得兩個名額可以探佢15分鐘，所以佢同牧師都等咗個半鐘見到快必。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。而且收押所食物比較差，快必每餐只係扒幾粒飯，所以佢個人都瘦咗，只係快必話唔介意。<br />\n<br />\n劉公子又引述快必呼籲市民唔可以唔出聲，仲要加油，劉公子亦答應快必，噚日去慢必陳志全代佢係觀塘及藍田開嘅「抗疫」街站撐場，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"06995da614b22061004e2bb2d409b4d95ef00145","tid":2201658,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34aeafe783c579cd0cdf86be837077715772fc87","tid":2201658,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522ed54451f4ab8629ef747faaaf5391b00303ef","tid":2201658,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b093f9474e5ab42ab2759dd2603b396f9bddda01","tid":2201658,"uid":61547,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"吹大左<br />\n拉幾日就瘦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}